# NAME: Microsoft China CDN
# AUTHOR: Codex
# UPDATED: 2026-06-14
# FORMAT: Surge Ruleset
# SOURCES: Microsoft Learn, SukkaW/Surge, blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script
# NOTE: Microsoft domains with Mainland China CDN delivery or China-operated service endpoints.
# NOTE: Includes Microsoft 365 and Azure China services operated by 21Vianet.
# NOTE: Azure China platform suffixes can also match third-party tenants hosted in that cloud.
# NOTE: Put Microsoft_CDN.list before Microsoft.list when Mainland China traffic should use DIRECT.

# China-operated and global endpoints required by Microsoft 365 in China
DOMAIN,activation.sls.microsoft.com
DOMAIN,crl.microsoft.com
DOMAIN,login.microsoftonline.com
DOMAIN,nexusrules.officeapps.live.com
DOMAIN,ntservicepack.microsoft.com
DOMAIN,odc.officeapps.live.com
DOMAIN,office15client.microsoft.com
DOMAIN,officeclient.microsoft.com
DOMAIN,ols.officeapps.live.com
DOMAIN,osi.office.net
DOMAIN,portal.partner.microsoftonline.cdnsvc.com
DOMAIN,roaming.officeapps.live.com

